oy Project]\n'''Field and Investigative Services'''\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/AirOps/AirOps.aspx Air Operations]\n:Bicycle Rapid Response\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/CINT/CINT.aspx Critical Incident Negotiation Team (CINT)]\n:Emergency Operations\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/EOD/EOD.aspx Explosive Ordnance Detail (Bomb Squad)]\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Off_Duty/OffDuty.aspx Off-Duty Employment]\n:Patrol Training\n:Regional Terrorism Threat Assessment Center (R.T.T.A.C)\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Search_and_Rescue/SAR.aspx Search and Rescue]\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/SED/SED.aspx Special Enforcement Detail]\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Volunteer_Services/Volunteers.aspx Volunteer Services]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Volunteer_Services/DART.aspx Drowning Accident Rescue Team (DART)]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Volunteer_Services/Explorers.aspx Explorers Program]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Reserves/Reserves.aspx Reserve Forces]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Volunteer_Services/VIPS.aspx Volunteers in Partnership with the Sheriff (V.I.P.S)]\n:\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Central/Central.aspx Central Division]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Central/Canine.aspx Canine]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Central/Florin.aspx Florin Service Center]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Central/Marine.aspx Marine Enforcement]\n::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/Central/RanchoMurieta.aspx Rancho Murieta Safety Center]\n::Walnut Grove Service Center\n:\n:[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/CID/CID.aspx Centralized Investigations Division]\n:::ACE (Auto Crimes Enforcement)\n:::[https://www.sacsheriff.com/Pages/Organization/CID/ChildAbuse.aspx Child Abuse